item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pia coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

Stylista!

The best hair and make-up salon around town. For the coolest treat and 2018 fashion trends in hair, you're in the right place.

Laced Wigs

Wigs have been used since antiquity as hairstyle and costume; ancient Egyptians wore wigs to shield their shaved heads from the sun.

Human Hair

Wigs were made of human, horse, and yak hair and sewn onto a frame with silken thread were meant to be obvious as wigs and not the wearers actual hair

Facials

There are different kinds of masks (e.g. cactus, cucumber, etc.) for different purposes: deep-cleansing, by penetrating the pores;

Our Stylists Products Our Stylists

Our stylists dazzle you with such incredible work while getting you comfortable all along.

Products

We only use top-notch products that are industry standard.

Our products protect your hair from breakages adnd loss.

About us

Stylista hair and make-up salon is pleased to serve Metro Detroit. Whether you are searching for a new look or day of pampering, our number one priority is to please you. Come in today and treat yourself to the beauty and relaxation you deserve.

Our services

Hair

Healthy hair is beautiful hair. We use top-quality products to strengthen and repair then cut, color or style your way.

Skin

Hydrated, smooth, firm and clean. Skilled estheticians get to know your skin and provide facials, peels, waxing and custom treatments.

Book an appointment

Book an appointment by phone or email.

Call us on 080reachus or email us on contact@stylistahairsalon.com
